data.title: 380 Lotz Ct, Wayland, MI 49348
data.meta_description: Zillow has 35 photos of this $314,900 3 beds, 2 baths, 1,735 Square Feet single family home located at 380 Lotz Ct, Wayland, MI 49348 built in 2024. MLS #24027974.
data.text: Welcome to a brand new 3 bedroom home at the end of a cul de sac backed into woods. The main floor has a kitchen, eating area, living room, pantry and owners suite with 2 closets with a full bath as well. The lower level has 2 bedrooms, family room, laundry and storage. Other perks: close to 131, shopping, schools, and much more. Call for a private showing today!
